🎯 GOAL

I am building a production-grade GitHub-style Markdown Navigator for DSA learning, with strict API protection and quota control to prevent GitHub API exhaustion.

This is NOT a GitHub clone — it is inspired by GitHub’s navigation and interaction patterns, but optimized for structured learning, not browsing.

This system must remain:
deterministic
quota-safe
session-locked
SPA-stable
production-grade


